items.title: Awesome Digital History
items.content_text:
### Archives and primary sources / Austria

*   [Digitarium](https://digitarium-app.acdh-dev.oeaw.ac.at/) - Digital edition of the historical Wiener Zeitung.
*   [Österreichische Mediathek](https://www.mediathek.at/) - The Austrian archive for sound recordings and videos from cultural and contemporary history.
*   [Wien Geschichte Wiki](https://www.geschichtewiki.wien.gv.at/Wien_Geschichte_Wiki) - It is based on the Historical Dictionary Vienna by Felix Czeike, currently there are 50,156 contributions and 12,510 images.

### Archives and primary sources / Europe

*   [Visual Archive Southeastern Europe](http://gams.uni-graz.at/context:vase) - Historical and contemporary visual materials from Southeastern Europe.

### Archives and primary sources / Switzerland

*   [swisscollections](https://swisscollections.ch/) - Meta search engine for historical and modern collections in Swiss libraries and archives.
items.content_html:
Archives and primary sources / Austria

  • Digitarium - Digital edition of the historical Wiener Zeitung.
  • Österreichische Mediathek - The Austrian archive for sound recordings and videos from cultural and contemporary history.
  • Wien Geschichte Wiki - It is based on the Historical Dictionary Vienna by Felix Czeike, currently there are 50,156 contributions and 12,510 images.

Archives and primary sources / Europe

  • Visual Archive Southeastern Europe - Historical and contemporary visual materials from Southeastern Europe.

Archives and primary sources / Switzerland

  • swisscollections - Meta search engine for historical and modern collections in Swiss libraries and archives.

items.title: Awesome Seml
items.content_text:
### Tooling

*   [Alibi Detect (⭐2.4k)](https://github.com/SeldonIO/alibi-detect) - Python library focused on outlier, adversarial and drift detection.
*   [PyTorch Lightning (⭐30k)](https://github.com/PyTorchLightning/pytorch-lightning) - The lightweight PyTorch wrapper for high-performance AI research. Scale your models, not the boilerplate.
*   [Robustness Metrics (⭐470)](https://github.com/google-research/robustness_metrics) - Lightweight modules to evaluate the robustness of classification models.
*   [Seldon Core (⭐4.6k)](https://github.com/SeldonIO/seldon-core) - An MLOps framework to package, deploy, monitor and manage thousands of production machine learning models on Kubernetes.
*   [Tensorflow Data Validation (TFDV) (⭐772)](https://github.com/tensorflow/data-validation) - Library for exploring and validating machine learning data. Similar to Great Expectations, but for Tensorflow data.
items.content_html:
Tooling

  • Alibi Detect (⭐2.4k) - Python library focused on outlier, adversarial and drift detection.
  • PyTorch Lightning (⭐30k) - The lightweight PyTorch wrapper for high-performance AI research. Scale your models, not the boilerplate.
  • Robustness Metrics (⭐470) - Lightweight modules to evaluate the robustness of classification models.
  • Seldon Core (⭐4.6k) - An MLOps framework to package, deploy, monitor and manage thousands of production machine learning models on Kubernetes.
  • Tensorflow Data Validation (TFDV) (⭐772) - Library for exploring and validating machine learning data. Similar to Great Expectations, but for Tensorflow data.

items.title: Awesome Python Scientific Audio
items.content_text:
### Audio Related Packages / Audio Dataset and Dataloaders

*   [musdb](http://dsdtools.readthedocs.io) [:octocat: (⭐177)](https://github.com/sigsep/sigsep-mus-db) [:package:](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/musdb) - Parse and process the MUSDB18 dataset.
*   [audiomate (⭐137)](https://github.com/ynop/audiomate) [:octocat: (⭐137)](https://github.com/ynop/audiomate) [:package:](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/audiomate/) - Loading different types of audio datasets.
*   [mirdata](https://mirdata.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) [:octocat: (⭐385)](https://github.com/mir-dataset-loaders/mirdata) [:package:](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mirdata) - Common loaders for Music Information Retrieval (MIR) datasets.
items.content_html:
Audio Related Packages / Audio Dataset and Dataloaders

  • musdb 🐙 (⭐177) 📦 - Parse and process the MUSDB18 dataset.
  • audiomate (⭐137) 🐙 (⭐137) 📦 - Loading different types of audio datasets.
  • mirdata 🐙 (⭐385) 📦 - Common loaders for Music Information Retrieval (MIR) datasets.
